<plot>This exclusive video contains previously unreleased material from Deep Purple's tours of Australia; including: Interviews from the Tour; Sunbury 1975 footage; Complete live versions of "Into The Fire", "When A Blind Man Cries" and "Seventh Heaven"; Live footage shot at the Brisbane and Adelaide Shows, from the April 1999 Tour; "Hey Hey It's Saturday" live performances and rehearsals; and lots of behind the scenes footage including Ian Gillan's Rainforest walk-about.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?051755</url></doc>
